caption: Check it out! This took about…2 semesters maybe 1 ½ semesters? Anyway, This is my Senior Thesis project! Since i’m studio art I had to create a focus for my project and mine was Concept art and World building so all of these pictures are interconnected in order to convey a unified and easily understood world.
